<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:05:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯数月来首次从拉法向以色列中部特拉维夫发射火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fires-rocket-barrage-from-rafah-at-tel-aviv-central-israel-for-first-time-in-months/0000018f-b4bb-d24f-a5df-feff56040000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，弹幕是从拉法发射的，哈马斯很快承认对火箭弹负责。以色列中部城市多枚火箭弹碎片落下，荷兹利亚一户住宅的屋顶被落下的火箭弹片损坏</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 13:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fires-rocket-barrage-from-rafah-at-tel-aviv-central-israel-for-first-time-in-months/0000018f-b4bb-d24f-a5df-feff56040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电影制片人用原始镜头与 10 月 7 日否认者作斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-film-producer-fighting-october-7-deniers/0000018f-a5d9-d1e2-a1ff-afff06390000</link><description>在制作了两部关于哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的纪录片之后，制作公司首席执行官梅尼·阿维拉姆 (Meny Aviram) 表示，他意识到必须立即讲述这个故事，并为将来保存更多纪录片</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 11:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-05-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-film-producer-fighting-october-7-deniers/0000018f-a5d9-d1e2-a1ff-afff06390000</guid></item><item><title>喜剧演员戴夫·查佩尔在阿联酋节目中表示以色列正在实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/dave-chappele-says-reasonable-things-but-we-have-to-report-on-them-because-he-said-israel/0000018f-b426-d8a2-a3cf-b4a75fca0000</link><description>在阿布扎比的一场单口喜剧表演中，美国喜剧演员戴夫·查佩尔 (Dave Chappelle) 因评论加沙战争而遭到欢呼和嘲笑，他表示“10 月 7 日发生的事情是不对的”，但“你不应该接受数十次”。我国投入数十亿资金去杀害无辜妇女和儿童</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 10:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/dave-chappele-says-reasonable-things-but-we-have-to-report-on-them-because-he-said-israel/0000018f-b426-d8a2-a3cf-b4a75fca0000</guid></item><item><title>海牙关于以色列的决定具有历史意义，但其意义取决于执行情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hague-decision-on-israel-is-historic-but-its-significance-depends-on-implementation/0000018f-b3de-dfc6-a3ef-b7de2d930000</link><description>这是国际法庭首次直接要求以色列停止对巴勒斯坦人的军事行动，但如果美国阻止，裁决将成为一纸空文；代价可能是几代人的更多流血以及全球对国际法的信任受到侵蚀</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 09:38:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/hague-decision-on-israel-is-historic-but-its-significance-depends-on-implementation/0000018f-b3de-dfc6-a3ef-b7de2d930000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院对加沙作出裁决后，以色列准备打“外交消耗战”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-diplomatic-war-of-attrition-following-icj-ruling-on-gaza/0000018f-b3b7-dfc6-a3ef-b7ffb5e70000</link><description>在国际法院裁定以色列必须停止在拉法的所有对巴勒斯坦人“造成可能造成物质毁灭的条件”的行动后，以色列很快声称“毁灭”过去不是、现在也不是他们的目标。以色列现在将针对其糟糕的公关、联合国和法院发动三线战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 08:32:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-prepares-for-diplomatic-war-of-attrition-following-icj-ruling-on-gaza/0000018f-b3b7-dfc6-a3ef-b7ffb5e70000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫地区火箭弹袭击后，国防部长表示以色列在拉法的任务“更加明确”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-live/idf-denies-hamas-claim-it-captured-israeli-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018f-b2cd-d390-ab8f-f3cdd0fb0000</link><description>救援部门表示，以色列中部地区有两人在火箭弹袭击后受轻伤。 据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，停火和人质释放谈判将于周二恢复。 以色列国防军否认哈马斯在加沙俘获以色列士兵的说法。加沙病毒视频 ■ 以色列国防军称袭击了黎巴嫩南部五个村庄的真主党目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-live/idf-denies-hamas-claim-it-captured-israeli-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018f-b2cd-d390-ab8f-f3cdd0fb0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的保镖称，即使在事故发生后，他仍命令司机违反交通法规</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-bodyguards-say-he-orders-drivers-to-violate-traffic-laws-even-after-accident/0000018f-b269-d1e2-a1ff-be6fbd190000</link><description>保镖告诉他们的主管，这种驾驶方式危及他们、本-格维尔部长和路上的任何其他人。上周，对本-格维尔的汽车闯红灯进入十字路口事故的调查结束，警方调查人员认为有足够的证据起诉他的司机</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-bodyguards-say-he-orders-drivers-to-violate-traffic-laws-even-after-accident/0000018f-b269-d1e2-a1ff-be6fbd190000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院的裁决不会立即改变加沙战争，但以色列仍面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/rafah-operation-advances-as-israel-faces-added-pressure-by-icj-ruling-to-end-the-war/0000018f-b179-dfc6-a3ef-b57daa210000</link><description>虽然没有立即采取行动遏制以色列国防军，但从长远来看，存在两个危险：人质危机未得到解决就强行停火，以及错过拜登政府关于美国-沙特-以色列全面协议的提议。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 03:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article/.premium/rafah-operation-advances-as-israel-faces-added-pressure-by-icj-ruling-to-end-the-war/0000018f-b179-dfc6-a3ef-b57daa210000</guid></item><item><title>遵守国际法院的命令是以色列避免成为贱民国家的最后机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/obeying-icj-order-is-israels-last-opportunity-to-save-itself-from-becoming-a-pariah-state/0000018f-b0d0-d8a2-a3cf-b4d34eb40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 21:31:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/obeying-icj-order-is-israels-last-opportunity-to-save-itself-from-becoming-a-pariah-state/0000018f-b0d0-d8a2-a3cf-b4d34eb40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议内塔